name: Courage
description:
Courage is the art that represents women's power.it also shows if a person has courage, sky is the limit of that person.  you can see the mixture of nature, wildlife, environment, and human correlation
which remind us of our duties about nature. Triangles with blue color show the oceans of the world and the aqua life.Leafs  are black & white because we are burning forests and cutting them rapidly. In one part you can see the blue eye lady which shows the patience of the woman. The bird is a symbol of freedom which shows the woman's freedom is still a myth in many areas of the world.
